    dc:description "FIGURE 6. The holotype of Buprestis (Akiyamaia) costipennis (Fairmaire, 1891) (female, Kashmir, MNHN, photo by Antoine Mantilleri). A–C, habitus; D, ovipositor; E, labels. A, dorsal view; B, lateral view; C–D, ventral view. Scale bars for A–C = 5.0 mm, for D = 2.0 mm." ;
